          <strong>
            <a href="https://app.paywithflash.com/signup?ref=837fa65af323b9b01dcbfccdb7d9f4e64d7a598daac25bbdf0fdc06e9d89bdd0" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              Klik her for at gå til PaywithFlash →
